data.description: Beautiful home boasting 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom. Upon entry, you'll find a spacious living and dining combo that offers a versatile and welcoming space for both relaxation and entertaining. A breakfast bar adds a touch of convenience and a seamless flow from the dining area to the kitchen. The kitchen is a true centerpiece, boasting an inviting island and beautiful granite countertops. It's not just a place for culinary endeavors but also a gathering spot for family and friends. Its modern design and practical layout make it a chef's dream. Both bathrooms have been remodeled, offering updated fixtures, cabinets, freshly painted, and beautiful quartz countertops ensuring a touch of luxury and contemporary design. The attention to detail doesn't stop there. All lights in the house have been replaced. Added feature, lights are also temperature adjustable. The trim has been carefully painted or replaced, adding a fresh and polished look to the interior. Several rooms have received a fresh coat of paint. Practicality and comfort extend to the exterior as well. The open deck has been replaced with durable composite wood, providing a low-maintenance outdoor space for relaxation and al fresco dining. A fire pit has been thoughtfully added, making the backyard an inviting oasis for gatherings and cozy evenings. For added privacy and security, the property is fully fenced in, ensuring a safe space for children and pets to play freely. This home seamlessly combines modern upgrades with classic charm, creating a haven that's perfect for those seeking comfort, style, and functionality.
